channel.description:
[url=http://www.documentingreality.com/forum/f10/some-emo-girl-needs-serious-help-11192/]Right here[/url] is where one of the topics about this girl takes place. The link above follows to a forum topic, and on that topic has pictures of a girl who took pictures of her cutting herself, and posted them on the internet. Caution: The pictures are VERY gory.
Caution #2: After I saw this, I couldn't eat dinner. <_<
